	3.elsif -> we use this if we have more than one condition 

	
	structure of elsif 

		if condition 
			code....
		elsif condition
			code..
		elsif condition
			code..
		else
			code..
		end


		ex - 3.0.1 :071 > x = "sam" 
 	=> "sam" 
	3.0.1 :072 > y = "sai"
	 => "sai" 
