2.Conditionals -> unless -> this is opposite of if statements
			 -> it act in same way putting not operator in if conditions

	structure of unless

	unless condition
		code...
	else
		code..
	end


	ex - 3.0.1 :025 > x = 12
	 => 12 
	3.0.1 :026 > unless x<12
	3.0.1 :027 >   print "hello"
	3.0.1 :028 > end
	hello => nil 
